'''Martha Buntwhistle''' was the alias used by a [[Gender/Legends|female]] member of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] who accompanied a Rebel [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] to the planet [[Harridan (planet)|Harridan]] to pay off a 25,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credit]] debt to [[Egot Pai-4-Yem]]. "[[Henry Buntwhistle]]," the smuggler, was told to book into the [[Lullaby Motel]] with a false wife under this name if he wanted to make contact with Egot.

